"""Set math channel, eres operator."""
with expected_protocol(ik.teledyne.MAUI, [init,
    "F1:DEFINE EQN,'ERES(C1)',BITS,0.5", "F1:DEFINE EQN,'ERES(C1)',BITS,3",
    "F1:DEFINE EQN,'ERES(C1)',BITS,0.5"], [], sep='\n') as osc:
    osc.math[0].operator.eres(0)
    osc.math[0].operator.eres(0, 3)
    osc.math[0].operator.eres(0, 28)
